" span__sm=\"12\"]\r\n\r\n[testimonial image=\"https://toyenkhanhhoa.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/52819944_2238512966470897_5672607085875953664_n-280x280.jpg\" image_width=\"121\" pos=\"center\" name=\"Vũ Thị Thanh Tâm\" company=\"Giám đốc Khải Hoàn Land Thủ Thiêm\"]\r\n\r\n<p>Công việc của tôi khá bận rộn bên ngoài, mặc dù đã tiết giảm thời gian và khá cầu toàn trong việc chăm sóc gia đình. Nhưng tôi vẫn rất hài lòng với sản phẩm yến làm sạch của Yến Vàng vì chất lượng, độ nguyên chất.</p>\r\n\r\n[/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[/row]\r\n[row]\r\n\r\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\r\n\r\n[testimonial image=\"https://toyenkhanhhoa.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/47248421_2352239861456051_3274436719478308864_n-280x280.jpg\" image_width=\"121\" pos=\"center\" name=\"Mark Jance\" company=\"Facebook\"]\r\n\r\n<p>The overall use of flatsome is very VERY useful. It lacks very few, if any, things! I loved it and have created my first ever website Punsteronline.com! Best yet, flatsome gets free updates that are great! (and the support is amazing as well!:)</p>\r\n\r\n[/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\r\n\r\n[testimonial image=\"https://toyenkhanhhoa.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/52047576_672957343121973_1690011335384891392_n-280x280.jpg\" image_width=\"121\" pos=\"center\" name=\"Mark Jance\" company=\"Facebook\"]\r\n\r\n<div class=\"e-box h-p2 -stacked -radius-none\">\r\n<p class=\"t-body h-my1\">This theme is amazing, you can customize EVERYTHING! The theme is a game changer for the Envato Market, can\'t wait for the future with Flatsome. Soo many good experiences from this, THANKS!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n[/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\r\n\r\n[testimonial image=\"https://toyenkhanhhoa.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1551758_1458821634339700_1713773134_n-280x280.jpg\" image_width=\"121\" pos=\"center\" name=\"MIRORIM\"]\r\n\r\n<p>Excellent work. Very good theme, No need support, works perfectly. Congratulations !! <br />Waiting for version 3.0. Very excited.</p>\r\n\r\n[/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n[/ux_slider]\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"Cẩm nang &amp; Tài liệu miễn phí\" icon=\"icon-star\" link_text=\"XEM TẤT CẢ\" link=\"/category/cam-nang-tai-lieu/\"]\r\n\r\n[blog_posts style=\"bounce\" columns__md=\"1\" cat=\"72\" posts=\"4\" show_date=\"false\" excerpt=\"false\" comments=\"false\" image_radius=\"2\" image_hover=\"zoom-fade\" text_align=\"left\" text_size=\"small\" class=\"blog-posts-home\"]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"Về yến sào\" icon=\"icon-star\" link_text=\"XEM TẤT CẢ\" link=\"/category/cam-nang-tai-lieu/\"]\r\n\r\n[blog_posts style=\"overlay\" type=\"row\" columns=\"3\" columns__md=\"1\" cat=\"72\" posts=\"3\" show_date=\"false\" excerpt=\"reveal\" comments=\"false\" image_radius=\"2\" image_hover=\"zoom-fade\" text_align=\"left\" text_size=\"small\" class=\"blog-posts-home\"]', 'Big Sale', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '77-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-11-09 20:01:03', '2020-11-09 13:01:03', '', 77, 'http://lararocket.local:88/2020/11/09/77-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
